Probably not.
 

00:17:46.859 --> 00:17:49.618
Do I like this music?
 

00:17:49.618 --> 00:17:51.630
Yeah, I really do like this
music.

00:17:51.630 --> 00:17:54.837
I love this music but I've
heard it a lot,

00:17:54.837 --> 00:17:58.358
and when I first heard it I
didn't like it.

00:17:58.358 --> 00:17:59.924
It's one of these things like
sort of aural spinach or

00:17:59.924 --> 00:18:00.250
